metadata.name: Octopussy Gang #1
metadata.description:
Welcome to the adventures of the Octopussy Gang! A collection of Cute Chibi Octopuss-Cat Hybrids or CatGirl-Octopuss Hybrids. They are cute but strong! Don't underestimate their abilities to take down the Evils that Lurk in Octopussy Lagoon! 

The Octopussy Gang is in Phase 1 with the first goal to build 1000 holders. Mint will cost 0.008 for the first 100 pieces. Additional listings will vary depending on intricacies. 

We are looking to build up our DEV Team & the ability for Holders to make passive income, If you or someone you know would like to apply to be part of our development team, please contact us via the linktree - Section Team applications

20% of all proceeds will be allocated for Newcollar.co After Phase 1 completion. 
5% of all proceeds will be allocated for ShibBurn Portal, After Phase 1 completion.
